<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Responsive Skincare AI</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/aos/2.3.4/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a076d05399.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <style>
        /* General Styles */
        img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        /* Typography */
        h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
        h2 { font-size: 2rem; }
        p { font-size: 1.1rem; }

        /* Buttons */
        .custom-link {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .custom-link:hover { background-color: #0056b3; }

        /* Animations */
        .fade-in { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease; }
        .fade-in.show { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    </style>
</head>
<body style="background-color:  #eceff1;">

    <%- include('navbar.ejs') %>

    <% if (messages.welcome && messages.welcome.length > 0) { %>
        <div class="alert alert-success welcome"><%= messages.welcome[0] %></div>
    <% } %>

    <% if (messages.error && messages.error.length > 0) { %>
        <div class="alert alert-danger error danger"><%= messages.error[0] %></div>
    <% } %>

    <!-- Main Container -->
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="row row1 align-items-center fade-in" data-aos="fade-up">
            <div class="col-md-6 text-center p-4">
                <img src="media/images/acne.jpg" class="img-fluid" style="width: 80%;"/>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 p-4">
                <h2>Revolutionizing Skincare with AI</h2>
                <p>Our project analyzes facial features to provide personalized skincare recommendations. 
                By leveraging advanced AI techniques, we can detect acne, wrinkles, dark circles, and more, offering 
                users insights into their skin health and potential vitamin deficiencies. Our approach ensures 
                that skincare is not just reactive but also proactive, helping individuals maintain optimal skin health.</p>
                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                    <li>✔️ AI-powered skin analysis</li>
                    <li>✔️ Personalized skincare insights</li>
                    <li>✔️ Face shape-based recommendations</li>
                    <li>✔️ Nutritional deficiency detection</li>
                    <li>✔️ Hair and grooming suggestions</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Personalized Health Insights Section -->
    <div class="container p-5">
        <div class="row row2 align-items-center fade-in" data-aos="fade-right">
            <div class="col-md-6 p-4">
                <h1>Personalized Health Insights</h1>
                <p>Our advanced analysis helps detect potential vitamin deficiencies by examining facial features,
                   enabling users to take proactive steps toward better health. With our AI-driven insights, 
                   users can make informed decisions about their skincare routine and overall well-being.</p>
                <p>We go beyond traditional skincare solutions by integrating scientific research with AI technology, 
                   ensuring that every recommendation is backed by data. Our system evaluates various parameters 
                   such as skin texture, hydration levels, and pigmentation to provide a comprehensive skincare assessment.</p>
                <a href="#" class="custom-link">Explore Your Health Insights</a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 p-4 text-center">
                <img src="media/images/removeacne.jpg" class="img-fluid" style="width: 60%;"/>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Look-Maxing Section -->
    <div class="container mb-5">
        <div class="row row3 align-items-center fade-in" data-aos="fade-left">
            <div class="col-md-6 p-4 text-center">
                <img src="media/images/lookmaxing.jpg" class="img-fluid" style="width: 90%;" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 p-4">
                <h1>Personalized Look-Maximization Guidance</h1>
                <p>Our advanced analysis helps you enhance your appearance by providing customized recommendations 
                   for skincare, grooming, and facial aesthetics. By assessing facial symmetry, skin texture, 
                   and hair density, we offer tailored suggestions to help you look and feel your best.</p>
                <p>Whether you’re looking for the best hairstyle to complement your face shape or seeking skincare 
                   routines to maintain a youthful appearance, our AI-driven guidance ensures you receive the 
                   best advice based on your unique features.</p>
                <a href="#" class="custom-link">Explore Your Best Look</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('footer.ejs') %>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/aos/2.3.4/aos.js"></script>
    <script>
        AOS.init();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
